: "Door", "part_of_speech": "noun (f)", "category": "Home", "cefr_level": "A1", "sentence_ru": "Дверь закрыта.", "sentence_en": "The door is closed.", "notes": "Soft sign at end → feminine."}, {"id": 27, "date": "2026-01-27", "word": "Машина", "pronunciation": "Ma-SHI-na", "ipa": "/mɐˈʂɨnə/", "meaning": "Car", "part_of_speech": "noun (f)", "category": "Transport", "cefr_level": "A1", "sentence_ru": "Это моя машина.", "sentence_en": "This is my car.", "notes": "Also literally 'machine'."}, {"id": 28, "date": "2026-01-28", "word": "Телефон", "pronunciation": "Tye-lye-FON", "ipa": "/tʲɪlʲɪˈfon/", "meaning": "Phone", "part_of_speech": "noun (m)", "category": "Objects", "cefr_level": "A1", "sentence_ru": "Мой телефон новый.", "sentence_en": "My phone is new.", "notes": "Cognate — easy to remember."}, {"id": 29, "date": "2026-01-29", "word": "Вода", "pronunciation": "Va-DA", "ipa": "/vɐˈda/", "meaning": "Water", "part_of_speech": "noun (f)", "category": "Food & Drink", "cefr_level": "A1", "sentence_ru": "Можно воды?", "sentence_en": "Can I have some water?", "notes": "Stress shifts in different cases."}, {"id": 30, "date": "2026-01-30", "word": "Хлеб", "pronunciation": "Khlyep", "ipa": "/xlʲep/", "meaning": "Bread", "part_of_speech": "noun (m)", "category": "Food & Drink", "cefr_level": "A1", "sentence_ru": "Свежий хлеб вкусный.", "sentence_en": "Fresh bread is delicious.", "notes": "Final 'б' devoiced to 'p'."}, {"id": 31, "date": "2026-01-31", "word": "Молоко", "pronunciation": "Ma-la-KO", "ipa": "/məlɐˈko/", "meaning": "Milk", "part_of_speech": "noun (n)", "category": "Food & Drink", "cefr_level": "A1", "sentence_ru": "Я люблю молоко.", "sentence_en": "I love milk.", "notes": "Three unstressed 'о's all sound different."}, {"id": 32, "date": "2026-02-01", "word": "Кофе", "pronunciation": "KO-fye", "ipa": "/ˈkofʲe/", "meaning": "Coffee", "part_of_speech": "noun (m)", "category": "Food & Drink", "cefr_level": "A1", "sentence_ru": "Чёрный кофе, пожалуйста.", "sentence_en":